<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Catfish escape -->
  <CatfishEscape.letterLabel>鲶鱼逃脱</CatfishEscape.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While attempting to wrangle a catfish, {PAWN_nameDef} stumbled and lost the slippery fish in the murky waters. -->
  <CatfishEscape.letterText>在试图捕捉一条鲶鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}失足，结果把滑溜的鱼儿弄丢在了浑浊的水中。</CatfishEscape.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Catfish spine -->
  <CatfishSpine.letterLabel>鲶鱼刺伤</CatfishSpine.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While handling a catfish, {PAWN_nameDef} was stung by one of the fish's toxic dorsal spines, causing {PAWN_objective} to drop the fish. -->
  <CatfishSpine.letterText>在处理鲶鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}被鱼有毒的背鳍刺到，结果{PAWN_objective}不得不丢下手中的鱼。</CatfishSpine.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Dogfish bite -->
  <DogfishBite.letterLabel>狗鱼咬伤</DogfishBite.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While reeling in a dogfish, {PAWN_nameDef} was bitten.\n\nThe fish managed to escape. -->
  <DogfishBite.letterText>在收线拉起狗鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}被咬了一口。\n\n鱼儿趁机逃脱了。</DogfishBite.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Dogfish escape -->
  <DogfishEscape.letterLabel>狗鱼逃脱</DogfishEscape.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While reeling in a dogfish, {PAWN_nameDef} nearly bitten by the thrashing creature.\n\nThe fish escaped in the confusion. -->
  <DogfishEscape.letterText>在收线拉起狗鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}差点被疯狂挣扎的鱼咬到。\n\n在混乱中，鱼儿溜走了。</DogfishEscape.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Flying frostfish -->
  <FrostfishAttack.letterLabel>霜鱼跃起</FrostfishAttack.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While fishing, {PAWN_nameDef} was suddenly hit by a frostfish leaping out of the water. This caused {PAWN_objective} to lose {PAWN_possessive} catch. -->
  <FrostfishAttack.letterText>在钓鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}突然被一条跃出水面的霜鱼击中，导致{PAWN_objective}失去了{PAWN_possessive}的渔获。</FrostfishAttack.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Guppy escape -->
  <GuppyEscape.letterLabel>孔雀鱼逃脱</GuppyEscape.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While attempting to catch a guppy, {PAWN_nameDef} fumbled the small slippery fish, allowing it to escape. -->
  <GuppyEscape.letterText>在试图抓住一条孔雀鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}没有抓稳这条滑溜的小鱼，让它逃脱了。</GuppyEscape.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Marlin attack -->
  <MarlinAttack.letterLabel>马林鱼袭击</MarlinAttack.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While fishing, {PAWN_nameDef} was attacked by a giant marlin and was skewered by its spear-like snout. The fish escaped. -->
  <MarlinAttack.letterText>在钓鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}被一条巨大的马林鱼袭击，并被它长矛般的吻部刺中。鱼儿逃脱了。</MarlinAttack.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Giant fish -->
  <MarlinEscape.letterLabel>巨型鱼影</MarlinEscape.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While fishing, {PAWN_nameDef} saw the shadow of a massive fish beneath the water. The shadow startled {PAWN_nameDef}, causing {PAWN_objective} to lose {PAWN_possessive} catch. -->
  <MarlinEscape.letterText>在钓鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}看到水下有一条庞大的鱼影。这一幕把{PAWN_nameDef}吓了一跳，使得{PAWN_objective}丢失了{PAWN_possessive}的渔获。</MarlinEscape.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Piranha attack -->
  <PiranhaAttack.letterLabel>食人鱼袭击</PiranhaAttack.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While fishing, {PAWN_nameDef} got too close to the water and was attacked by a frenzied school of piranha!\n\nThe fish managed to escape. -->
  <PiranhaAttack.letterText>在钓鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}靠水太近，被一群疯狂的食人鱼袭击了！\n\n鱼儿趁机逃脱了。</PiranhaAttack.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Piranha bite -->
  <PiranhaBite.letterLabel>食人鱼咬伤</PiranhaBite.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While fishing, {PAWN_nameDef} got too close to the water and was bitten by a piranha!\n\nThe fish escaped. -->
  <PiranhaBite.letterText>在钓鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}靠水太近，被一条食人鱼咬了一口！\n\n鱼儿逃脱了。</PiranhaBite.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: Tuna escape -->
  <TunaEscape.letterLabel>金枪鱼逃脱</TunaEscape.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: While attempting to reel in a tuna, {PAWN_nameDef}'s line snapped, causing {PAWN_objective} to lose the catch. -->
  <TunaEscape.letterText>在试图拉上金枪鱼时，{PAWN_nameDef}的鱼线断裂，导致{PAWN_objective}丢失了渔获。</TunaEscape.letterText>
  
</LanguageData>